WITH hourly_sales AS (
    SELECT 
        date_trunc('hour', CAST(timestamp AS TIMESTAMP)) AS hour,
        category,
        SUM(amount) AS total_sales
    FROM sales
    GROUP BY 1, 2
)
SELECT 
    hour,
    COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN category = 'Electronics' THEN total_sales END), 0) AS Electronics,
    COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN category = 'Clothing' THEN total_sales END), 0) AS Clothing,
    COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN category = 'Furniture' THEN total_sales END), 0) AS Furniture,
    COALESCE(SUM(CASE WHEN category = 'Toys' THEN total_sales END), 0) AS Toys
FROM hourly_sales
GROUP BY hour
ORDER BY hour;
